    <abstract id="aspace_f6e942e2eaae80777a60a9068f4a0d58">Barbara Schultz (1927-2019) was a television producer and oversaw shows such as <title>CBS Playhouse</title>, PBS's <title>Visions</title>, and <title>You Are There</title>. Collection materials consist of scripts and production notes for the programs Schultz produced including <title>CBS Playhouse</title> and <title>You Are There</title>. Materials also include datebooks, address books, correspondence, photographs, and staging plans. The materials date from 1950 to 2006.</abstract>
